extends layout

block content
  div(class="container mx-auto px-6 py-8")
    // Hero Header
    section(class="mb-12 relative overflow-hidden")
      div(class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-500/10 via-rose-500/10 to-red-500/10 rounded-3xl")
      div(class="relative bg-gradient-to-r from-white/80 to-white/60 dark:from-gray-800/80 dark:to-gray-700/60 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-3xl p-8 border border-white/20 dark:border-gray-600/30")
        div(class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center")
          div(class="mb-6")
            div(class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-rose-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4 animate-float")
              svg(class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24")
                path(stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z")
              span Temukan Anime Favorit
          h1(class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 leading-tight")
            span(class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100") Pencarian 
            span(class="gradient-text") Anime
          p(class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto") Cari dan temukan anime favorit Anda dengan mudah. Gunakan kata kunci yang spesifik untuk hasil yang lebih akurat.

    div(class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8")
      div(class="lg:col-span-3")
        // Search Form
        div(class="mb-8")
          form(action="/search" method="GET" class="relative group")
